sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Form as Communications Form
    participant API as /api/send-email
    participant SES as AWS SES<br/>(eu-west-2)
    participant Recipient as Sky UK Recipient

    User->>Form: 1. Fill Communication Form
    User->>Form: 2. Click "Send via AWS SES"
    Form->>Form: 3. generateEmailHTML()
    Note over Form: Creates styled HTML<br/>with gradients, sections,<br/>contact info (~7500 chars)
    Form->>API: 4. POST /api/send-email<br/>{to, subject, htmlContent}
    API->>API: 5. Load SES credentials<br/>(SES_* env vars)
    API->>API: 6. AWS Signature V4 signing
    API->>SES: 7. POST /v2/email/outbound-emails
    SES->>API: 8. 200 OK + MessageId
    API->>Form: 9. Success response
    Form->>User: 10. Show success toast
    SES->>Recipient: 11. Deliver formatted HTML email
